### Upload Petstore Spec (from file - use in IDE)
POST http://localhost:8090/api/spec/upload
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="petstore.yaml"
Content-Type: application/x-yaml

< ./src/main/resources/petstore.yaml
--boundary--

